title: Backstreet Boys - In A World Like This (CDS)
description:
"In a World Like This" is a song by American pop group Backstreet Boys from their upcoming eighth studio album, In a World Like This. It is set to be released as the album's lead single on June 25, 2013 as a digital download and July 3, 2013 on CD in Japan. The song was written by Kristian Lundin, Max Martin, Savan Kotecha, and it was produced by Martin and Lundin. It is the group's first lead single to be written by long-time collaborator Max Martin since "Shape of My Heart" (2000).
